This will allow users to copy paste code conventions into git hub pull request comments easily.

You can configure it yourself as long as your object structure is as follows (or imitate the existing default object):
{
    'RowHeader': [
        'CodeConvention-1': {
            'code': 'Code to display',
            'name': 'Name of code',
            'link': 'Link to this convention'
        },
        'CodeConvention-2': {
            'code': 'Code to display',
            'name': 'Name of code',
            'link': 'Link to this convention'
        },
    ],
}
